"description\": \"Understand how to use microservices architecture\", \"key_concepts\": \"microservices,architecture,scalability\"}, {\"title\": \"Cloud Native Architecture\", \"duration\": \"2h\", \"description\": \"Get introduced to cloud native architecture\", \"key_concepts\": \"cloud native,architecture,scalability\"}]}, {\"title\": \"Career Development and Production\", \"accent_color\": \"#6C63FF\", \"topics\": [{\"title\": \"Resume Building and Interview Preparation\", \"duration\": \"2h\", \"description\": \"Learn how to build a strong resume and prepare for interviews\", \"key_concepts\": \"resume,interview,preparation\"}, {\"title\": \"Production Environment and Deployment\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Understand how to deploy and manage production environments\", \"key_concepts\": \"production,environment,deployment\"}, {\"title\": \"Career Growth and Professional Development\", \"duration\": \"2h\", \"description\": \"Explore ways to grow and develop professionally in devops\", \"key_concepts\": \"career,growth,professional development\"}]}], \"source\": \"AI Generated\"}', '2026-03-24 09:25:14'),
