(31, 4, 'Data Analyst', '{\"goal_title\": \"Data Analyst\", \"description\": \"A massive exhaustive path for AI and Data Science experts.\", \"modules\": [{\"title\": \"Math & Statistics Concepts\", \"accent_color\": \"#4F8EF7\", \"topics\": [{\"title\": \"Linear Algebra (Vectors, Matrices)\", \"duration\": \"25m\", \"description\": \"Linear Algebra (Vectors, Matrices) is a cornerstone concept for this track. Mastering this topic provides the foundation for building scalable, maintainable, and high-performance applications.\\n\\nTake your time reading through the curriculum material. After you grasp the theory, review the curated resources linked below, and consult the AI Tutor to run through personalized example scenarios and practice problems.\", \"key_concepts\": \"\\u2022 Core Mechanics\\n\\u2022 Performance Constraints\\n\\u2022 Trade-offs & Anti-patterns\\n\\u2022 Best Practices\\n\\u2022 Real-world usage\\n\\u2022 Common pitfalls to avoid\"}, {\"title\": \"Calculus Fundamentals\", \"duration\": \"25m\", \"description\": \"Calculus Fundamentals is a cornerstone concept for this track. Mastering this topic provides the foundation for building scalable, maintainable, and high-performance applications.\\n\\nTake your time reading through the curriculum material. After you grasp the theory, review the curated resources linked below, and consult the AI Tutor to run through personalized example scenarios and practice problems.\", \"key_concepts\": \"\\u2022 Core Mechanics\\n\\u2022 Performance Constraints\\n\\u2022 Trade-offs & Anti-patterns\\n\\u2022 Best Practices\\n\\u2022 Real-world usage\\n\\u2022 Common pitfalls to avoid\"}, {\"title\": \"Probability Distributions\", \"duration\": \"25m\", \"description\": \"Probability Distributions is a cornerstone concept for this track. Mastering this topic provides the foundation for building scalable, maintainable, and high-performance applications.\\n\\nTake your time reading through the curriculum material. After you g