searching\", \"id\": \"35_sorting_and_searching_algorithms\"}, {\"title\": \"Dynamic Programming\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about dynamic programming techniques.\", \"key_concepts\": \"dynamic programming, optimization, algorithms\", \"id\": \"35_dynamic_programming\"}]}, {\"title\": \"System Design and Cloud\", \"accent_color\": \"#F59E0B\", \"topics\": [{\"title\": \"Introduction to System Design\", \"duration\": \"2h\", \"description\": \"Learn the basics of system design for building scalable systems.\", \"key_concepts\": \"system design, scalability, architecture\", \"id\": \"35_introduction_to_system_design\"}, {\"title\": \"Cloud Computing with AWS\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn the basics of cloud computing using AWS.\", \"key_concepts\": \"AWS, cloud computing, infrastructure\", \"id\": \"35_cloud_computing_with_aws\"}, {\"title\": \"Microservices Architecture\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about microservices architecture for building scalable systems.\", \"key_concepts\": \"microservices, architecture, scalability\", \"id\": \"35_microservices_architecture\"}, {\"title\": \"Containerization with Docker\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about containerization using Docker for deployment.\", \"key_concepts\": \"Docker, containerization, deployment\", \"id\": \"35_containerization_with_docker\"}, {\"title\": \"Kubernetes Introduction\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn the basics of Kubernetes for orchestrating containers.\", \"key_concepts\": \"Kubernetes, container orchestration, deployment\", \"id\": \"35_kubernetes_introduction\"}]}, {\"title\": \"Advanced Topics\", \"accent_color\": \"#F97316\", \"topics\": [{\"title\": \"Machine Learning Introduction\", \"duration\": \"2h\", \"description\": \"Learn the basics of machine learning for building predictive models.\", \"key_concepts\": \"machine learning, predictive models, algorithms\", \"id\": \"35_machine_learning_introduction\"}, {\"title\": \"Web Security and Authentication\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about web security and authentication techniques.\", \"key_concepts\": \"web security, authentication, authorization\", \"id\": \"35_web_security_and_authentication\"}, {\"title\": \"Testing and Deployment\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about testing and deployment strategies for software development.\", \"key_concepts\": \"testing, deployment, CI/CD\", \"id\": \"35_testing_and_deployment\"}, {\"title\": \"DevOps and Agile Methodologies\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about DevOps and Agile methodologies for software development.\", \"key_concepts\": \"DevOps, Agile, software development\", \"id\": \"35_devops_and_agile_methodologies\"}, {\"title\": \"Cloud Native Applications\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about cloud native applications and their benefits.\", \"key_concepts\": \"cloud native, applications, benefits\", \"id\": \"35_cloud_native_applications\"}]}, {\"title\": \"Career Development\", \"accent_color\": \"#8B5CF6\", \"topics\": [{\"title\": \"Resume Building and Interview Preparation\", \"duration\": \"2h\", \"description\": \"Learn how to build a strong resume and prepare for technical interviews.\", \"key_concepts\": \"resume, interview, preparation\", \"id\": \"35_resume_building_and_interview_preparation\"}, {\"title\": \"Networking and Community Building\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about the importance of networking and community building for career development.\", \"key_concepts\": \"networking, community, career development\", \"id\": \"35_networking_and_community_building\"}, {\"title\": \"Personal Branding and Online Presence\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about personal branding and online presence for career development.\", \"key_concepts\": \"personal branding, online presence, career development\", \"id\": \"35_personal_branding_and_online_presence\"}, {\"title\": \"Continuous Learning and Professional Development\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about the importance of continuous learning and professional development for career growth.\", \"key_concepts\": \"continuous learning, professional development, career growth\", \"id\": \"35_continuous_learning_and_professional_development\"}, {\"title\": \"Job Search Strategies and Salary Negotiation\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about job search strategies and salary negotiation techniques.\", \"key_concepts\": \"job search, salary negotiation, career development\", \"id\": \"35_job_search_strategies_and_salary_negotiation\"}]}, {\"title\": \"Production and Deployment\", \"accent_color\": \"#EF4444\", \"topics\": [{\"title\": \"CI/CD Pipelines with Jenkins\", \"duration\": \"2h\", \"description\": \"Learn about CI/CD pipelines using Jenkins for automated deployment.\", \"key_concepts\": \"Jenkins, CI/CD, pipelines\", \"id\": \"35_ci/cd_pipelines_with_jenkins\"}, {\"title\": \"Containerization with Docker\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about containerization using Docker for deployment.\", \"key_concepts\": \"Docker, containerization, deployment\", \"id\": \"35_containerization_with_docker\"}, {\"title\": \"Kubernetes Deployment\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about Kubernetes deployment for orchestrating containers.\", \"key_concepts\": \"Kubernetes, deployment, containers\", \"id\": \"35_kubernetes_deployment\"}, {\"title\": \"Monitoring and Logging with Prometheus and Grafana\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about monitoring and logging using Prometheus and Grafana.\", \"key_concepts\": \"Prometheus, Grafana, monitoring, logging\", \"id\": \"35_monitoring_and_logging_with_prometheus_and_grafana\"}, {\"title\": \"Security and Compliance in Production\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about security and compliance in production environments.\", \"key_concepts\": \"security, compliance, production\", \"id\": \"35_security_and_compliance_in_production\"}]}, {\"title\": \"Final Project and Review\", \"accent_color\": \"#3B82F6\", \"topics\": [{\"title\": \"Final Project Development\", \"duration\": \"1 week\", \"description\": \"Work on a final project to apply the skills learned throughout the roadmap.\", \"key_concepts\": \"final project, application, skills\", \"id\": \"35_final_project_development\"}, {\"title\": \"Review and Reflection\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Review and reflect on the skills learned throughout the roadmap.\", \"key_concepts\": \"review, reflection, skills\", \"id\": \"35_review_and_reflection\"}, {\"title\": \"Career Development and Next Steps\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about next steps for career development and growth.\", \"key_concepts\": \"career development, next steps, growth\", \"id\": \"35_career_development_and_next_steps\"}, {\"title\": \"Continuous Learning and Improvement\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn about the importance of continuous learning and improvement for career growth.\", \"key_concepts\": \"continuous learning, improvement, career growth\", \"id\": \"35_continuous_learning_and_improvement\"}, {\"title\": \"Final Assessment and Evaluation\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Complete a final assessment and evaluation to measure progress and skills.\", \"key_concepts\": \"final assessment, evaluation, skills\", \"id\": \"35_final_assessment_and_evaluation\"}]}], \"source\": \"AI Generated\", \"is_saved\": true, \"id\": \"35\"}', '2026-03-31 09:13:21');
