gorithms in C#\", \"key_concepts\": \"sorting, searching, algorithms\", \"id\": \"38_sorting_and_searching_algorithms\"}, {\"title\": \"Big-O notation\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Understand the basics of Big-O notation for algorithm complexity\", \"key_concepts\": \"Big-O notation, time complexity, space complexity\", \"id\": \"38_big-o_notation\"}]}, {\"title\": \"Databases and Cloud\", \"accent_color\": \"#10B981\", \"topics\": [{\"title\": \"Introduction to SQL Server\", \"duration\": \"2h\", \"description\": \"Learn the basics of SQL Server for database management\", \"key_concepts\": \"SQL Server, database management, queries\", \"id\": \"38_introduction_to_sql_server\"}, {\"title\": \"Azure Cosmos DB\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Understand the basics of Azure Cosmos DB for NoSQL database management\", \"key_concepts\": \"Azure Cosmos DB, NoSQL, document database\", \"id\": \"38_azure_cosmos_db\"}, {\"title\": \"Azure Storage\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Learn how to use Azure Storage for cloud storage\", \"key_concepts\": \"Azure Storage, blob storage, file storage\", \"id\": \"38_azure_storage\"}, {\"title\": \"Introduction to Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS)\", \"duration\": \"1 day\", \"description\": \"Understand the basics of AKS for container orchestration\", \"key_concepts\": \"AKS, container orchestration, Kubernetes\", \"id\": \"38_introduction_to_azure_kubernetes_service_(aks)\"}]}, {\"title\": \"Advanced Topics\", \"accent_color\": \"#F59E0B\", \"topics\": [{\"title\": \"ASP.NET Core Identity\", \"duration\": \"2h\", \"description\": \"Learn how to use ASP.NET Core Identity for authentication and authorization\", \"key_concepts\": \"ASP.NET Core Identity, authentication, authorization\", \"id\": \"38_asp.net_core_identity\"}, {\"title\": \"ASP.NET Core SignalR\", \"duration\": \"2h\", \"description\": \"Understand how to use ASP.NET Core SignalR for real-time web functionality\", \"key_concepts\":